!S. Fartoukh, readme file for the 2018 round optics MDs, 24/05/2018

*** SHORT DESCRIPTION
a) The ramp is NEW: Combined Ramp and Double Squeeze (CRDS)
- opticsfile.1 to opticsfile.18
-> opticsfile.1  (inj)   to opticsfile.11 (2.30 m) are nominal pre-squeezed optics
-> opticsfile.12 (2.0 m) to opticsfile.18 (0.65 m) describe a tele-squeeze to reach a tele-index of 2/0.65 ~ 3 at the end of ramp
- LSA Beam Process under construction

b) The squeeze is new (restarting the pre-squeeze sequence from 2.0 m to 77 cm, at constant tele-index)
- opticsfile.18 (65.000 cm) to opticsfile.25 (25.025 cm = 0.65/2 * 77 cm)
- LSA Beam Process under construction


**** DEFAULT SETTINGS for KNOB values:
a) Energy defined to 6.5 TeV in all optics files

b) Tunes matched to 62.31/60.32 for all optics files

c) Chroma matched to 2 units for all optics
   
d) IP crossing knob (on_x1/2/5/6) calibrated in microrad and set to end of ramp values in all optics files
   (namely, on_x1=on_x5=160, on_x2=200, on_x8=-250)
   
e) IP parallel sep knob (on_sep1/2/5/8) calibrated in mm and set to end of ramp values in all optics files
   (namely, on_sep1=-0.55, on_sep5=0.55,on_sep2=1, on_sep8=-1)
   
g) IP shift knob (on_oh/v/1/2/5/8) calibrated in mm set to the collision value in all optics files,
   namely on_ov2=-2 (Alice IP shift), and on_ov5=-1.8 (CMS IP shift)

**** OPTICS FILE NAMING CONVENTION  !!!!!!! for upload in LSA, only files with "_LSA" suffix should be used !!!!!
